headline: OXIO Surpasses 2 Million Activated Lines in North America, Signaling Growth in Telecom-as-a-Service (TaaS)
summary: NEW YORK, July 16, 2025--OXIO, a leading Telecom-as-a-Service (TaaS) platform, today announced it has surpassed 2 million activated lines on its wholesale network across North America, marking a key milestone in the company’s expansion.
